Product Description

The availability of this product is limited and subject to change.Wine Tasting NotesDeep, dark red in color with elegant notes of plum and black cherry followed by subtle nuances of caraway and black pepper. On the palate, it is fresh, full and juicy with solid mid palate weight and an expansive, round finish.
	







